#: app/ai.php:582
msgid "Analyze product images and related descriptions to generate high-quality, engaging, and SEO-optimized product content. Focus on identifying key visual details such as type, color, material, and purpose to create accurate, natural, and persuasive descriptions suitable for e-commerce platforms."
msgstr "分析产品图像和相关描述，以生成高质量、吸引人且 SEO 优化的产品内容。重点识别关键视觉细节，如类型、颜色、材质和用途，以创建准确、自然且具有说服力的描述，适用于电子商务平台。"

#: app/ai.php:589
msgid "Review the provided product image and its details to understand the item’s appearance, features, and intended use. Then generate a compelling product title, short summary, detailed description, and a list of relevant SEO keywords based on your analysis."
msgstr "查看提供的产品图像及其细节，以了解物品的外观、功能和预期用途。然后根据您的分析生成吸引人的产品标题、简短摘要、详细描述以及相关 SEO 关键词列表。"

